item.title: Usher Gets Visibly Emotional During Final Show of Las Vegas Residency
item.description: Usher was visibly emotional while performing on stage during his 100th and final show for his My Way Las Vegas residency. The singer, 45, dropped to his knees and placed his face in his hands while performing “Without You,” per fan footage on Saturday, December 2. Usher’s dancers surrounded him on stage and cheered him on. After a few beats, Usher stood up, but quickly turned his back to the crowd as his dancers circled him and patted him on the shoulder.

item.title: Gina Rodriguez Apologizes For Using N-Word: Watch
item.description: Gina Rodriguez is saying sorry after receiving backlash for using the n-word in a video where she raps along to the Fugees song, “Ready or Not.” The Jane the Virgin star deleted the controversial recording from her Instagram stories on Tuesday (Oct. 15), and replaced it with an apology video. “I just wanted to reach out and apologize. I am sorry if I offended anyone by singing along to the Fugees,” Rodriguez said, before adding that she grew up on the song and loves Lauryn Hill.

item.title: Man City blow as star defenders Ruben Dias and John Stones ruled out of Burnley clash for Premier Le
item.description: Manchester City were forced to shuffle up their backline as Ruben Dias and John Stones were left out of their matchday squad that beat Burnley 3-0. Meanwhile the Citizens also left new signing Josko Gvardiol on the bench for the Turf Moor clash following his £77million switch from RB Leipzig, though he did make his debut in the second half. Pep Guardiola's side kicked-off their Premier League campaign away at Burnley with an easy 3-0 victory on Friday night, with Erling Haaland scoring twice and Rodri also getting on the score sheet.

item.title: Sean 'Diddy' Combs Regains Ownership Of Sean John For $7.5 Million
item.description: Sean 'Diddy' Combs agreed to pay $7.5 million in order to buy back the fashion brand he used to own after he won a court-supervised auction. The bankrupt fashion brand is currently owned by the brand manager GBG USA Inc. According to the submitted documents to the court, the company has made about 85% of its money by selling clothes and footwear through the retailers such as TJ Maxx, Costco, and Nordstrom.

item.title: Snooki Welcomes A Baby Boy, Lorenzo Dominic LaValle
item.description: Nicole “Snooki” Polizzi is officially a mother. The “Snooki & JWOWW” star gave birth to a boy shortly before 3AM on Sunday, at Saint Barnabas Medical Center in Livingston, N.J. “I am SO IN LOVE with my son Lorenzo Dominic ! I had my little man last night, healthy at 6lbs! HE’S MY WORLD!” Snooki tweeted shortly before 9 AM Sunday. The baby entered the world weighing 6 lbs, 5 oz.

item.title: The Full Story Of Why Matthew Underwood From 'Zoey 101' Was Arrested
item.description: Back in 2012, Matthew Underwood, the hunk of the popular Nickelodeon series Zoey 101, went through a rough patch. Underwood made headlines for all the wrong reasons but has since recovered from all the backlash. After almost a decade, we are diving back into what happened all those years ago. There would be no celebrity Matthew Underwood without the comedy-drama, Zoey 101 so let's start from there. This show put Underwood on the map and ran for a total of four seasons from 2005-2008.

item.title: Travis Scott Allegedly Cheated On Kylie Jenner And Adamantly Denies The Rumors
item.description: American rapper, singer, and record producer Travis Scott has denied wrongdoing after finding himself immersed in a cheating scandal involving a familiar face. Travis Scott's reported ex, Rojean Kar, has responded to claims that she and Travis have been hanging out - while the rapper is currently dating Kylie Jenner, according to Cosmopolitan. Instagram model Rojean was first linked to Travis back in 2013, according to reports. Then, in 2019, rumours claimed that Rojean was the reason for Kylie and Travis' split at the time, with Rojean denying any speculation.

item.title: Welsh Actor Michael Sheen Returns Order Of The British Empire Honor
item.description: Welsh actor Michael Sheen has returned his Order of the British Empire (OBE) honor given to him by Queen Elizabeth due to his opposition to the monarchy. The actor, who received the OBE in 2009 for services to drama, objects to the practice of bestowing the title of Prince of Wales to the heir apparent to the English throne. In an online interview, Sheen said he decided it would be hypocritical to keep the honor after considering the history of Wales and its centuries-old practice of simply handing the title of Prince of Wales to the heir apparent to the English throne.

item.description: Lindsey Shaw revealed her personal life was the reason behind her Pretty Little Liars character Paige McCullers’ departure from the hit series. “I got basically let go from Pretty Little Liars in season 5 because of the weight that I had lost, and it was really an embarrassing thing,” the 34-year-old actress shared on the Wednesday, July 5, episode of the “Ned’s Declassified Podcast Survival Guide” podcast. “I didn’t look good too skinny and then, you know, then when I started to put the weight back on, I couldn’t handle it being too heavy, so it kind of played into this dumb cycle.

item.title: Trey Hendrickson Injury Update: Bengals Star DE Expected to Play Against Bills
item.description: Trey Hendrickson is a professional American football defensive end for the Cincinnati Bengals of the National Football League. He was born on December 5, 1994, and attended Florida Atlantic University from 2013 to 2016. Hendrickson joined the NFL in 2017 after the New Orleans Saints selected him in the third round of the draft. He played for the Saints until 2020. He joined the Cincinnati Bengals in 2021 and has been an active member of their roster ever since.

item.title: Zoey Stark And Gigi Dolin Qualify For NXT Womens Title Ladder Match At NXT Stand And Deliver
item.description: Two WWE NXT stars have qualified for NXT Stand and Deliver. In the wake of reigning champion Roxanne Perez’s uncertain medical status, WWE began holding qualifying matches on March 14 to determine who would compete in a Ladder Match for the NXT Women’s Championship at Stand and Deliver on April 1. In the first qualifying bout, Zoey Stark emerged victorious over Sol Ruca. Later on, Gigi Dolin pinned Kiana James to earn her spot in the bout.

item.title: 'Squid Game' Reality Show Has A $4.56M Prize
item.description: Highlights Squid Game became a viral hit for its relatable themes of wealth, debt, and desperation, appealing to viewers worldwide. item.title: What is the significance of the two membranes which surround the lungs
item.description: What are the two membranes surrounding the lungs? The pleura includes two thin layers of tissue that protect and cushion the lungs. The inner layer (visceral pleura) wraps around the lungs and is stuck so tightly to the lungs that it cannot be peeled off. The outer layer (parietal pleura) lines the inside of the chest wall. Why is it important that there are two pleural membranes? Each pleural cavity and it’s enclosed lung are lined by a serous membrane called pleura.
